Definition: brusque and surly and forbidding
Example: crusty remarks; a crusty old man; his curmudgeonly temper; gruff manner; a gruff reply
Synonyms: noun, attribute, crust, curmudgeonly, person, curmudgeon, gruff, gruffness, ill-humored, ill-humoured, brusque, and, surly, forbidding, remarks, a, old, man, his, temper, manner, reply
Category: adj.all
